  <brief_title>Effect of Sevoflurane, Propofol and Dexmedetomidine on Delirium &amp; Neuroinflammation in Mechanically Ventilated Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Sedative Effects of Sevoflurane, Propofol and Dexmedetomidine on the Clinical Course of Delirium and Neuroinflammation in Mechanically Ventilated Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
